Package: xapr
Title: Access the Xapian search engine from R
Description: xapr is a package that provides an interface to the
    Xapian search engine from R, allowing both indexing and retrievel
    operations. NOTE: The package is in a very early development phase
    and not functional yet.
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Stefan", "Widgren", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "stefan.widgren@gmail.com"))
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2)
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/stewid/xapr
Type: Package
BugReports: https://github.com/stewid/xapr/issues
LazyData: true
Biarch: true
NeedsCompilation: yes
Date: 2014-09-12
Collate:
    'index.r'
    'search.r'
    'xapr.r'
